```

## Accessibility Notes

- Radix Collapsible automatically manages `aria-expanded` on the trigger
- Radix Collapsible automatically manages `aria-controls` pointing to the content
- The trigger is a `<button>` element, so it receives focus and responds to Enter/Space
- The chevron rotates via CSS `data-[state=open]:rotate-90` (Radix sets `data-state` automatically)
- Explicitly chosen over HoverCard which Radix documents as "inaccessible to keyboard users"
- Explicitly chosen over Tooltip which is wrong for multi-line content

